  "desc": "The MIT Committee on Prehealth Advising has provided the following information to guide MIT students on how to fulfill the academic requirements for admission to most U.S. medical schools. Specific requirements may vary for a particular school, and thus we suggest also referring to the Medical School Admission Requirements (MSAR) and information directly from particular schools to which you plan to apply."
